Purpose: A program that simulates a pit game where 2 heros randomly move in a map with randomly moving monsters and they try to escape without dying.

Source Files: defs.h Escape.h Escape.cc Hero.h Hero.cc PartArray.h PartArray.cc Participant.h Participant.cc Pit.h Pit.cc Position.h Position.cc random.cc Snorc.h Snorc.cc MakeFile

Launch Instructions:-
1.)Have all files mentioned above in the same directory
2.)In terminal enter the following command in the same directory; "make"
3.)Now enter "./test" to run the program
